description: Experience unparalleled accuracy in astrology and tarot readings with Tarot Master. Chat with your personal expert astrologers and tarot readers, each in-tune with your unique astrological data for highly personalized insights.

Tailored insights based on astrological data

faqs.question: Can I use your app if I'm new to tarot or astrology?
faqs.answer: Yes, our app is designed for users of all levels, including beginners in tarot and astrology.

faqs.question: How do you ensure the privacy and confidentiality of my readings?
faqs.answer: We prioritize the privacy of our users and ensure that all readings are confidential and secure.

faqs.question: What is the pricing structure for your readings? Are there additional costs?
faqs.answer: Our pricing is subscription-based with no additional costs. Users can access all features with their subscription.
